quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  18,62,"Naizvozvo pavakapfurira, Musa akati kune murandakomana wake: “Huya nechikafu chedu chemangwanani, zvirokwazvo, taneta zvakanyanya kubva murwendo rwedu urwu.”"
  18,63,"Akati: “Unoyeuka here patazorora padombo? Zvirokwazvo, ndakanganwa hove, hapana umwe asi Satani andiita kuti ndikanganwe kuzvirangarira. Uye yakatora nzira yayo mugungwa nenzira inoshamisa!”"
  18,64,"Musa akati: “Ndipo patiri kutsvaga.” Naizvozvo vakadzokera shure vachironda mitsindo yavo"
  18,65,"Naizvozvo vakawana muranda kubva kuvaranda vedu, uyo atakamupa tsitsi kubva kwatiri, uye tikamudzidzisa ruzivo kubva kwatiri"
  18,66,"Musa akati kwaari (Al-Khidr): “Ndikutevere here kuti undidzidzise zvimwe zveruzivo rwawakadzidziswa (naAllah)?”"
  18,67,"Akati (Al-Khidr): “Zvirokwazvo, haukwanisi kutsungirira neni!”"
  18,68,“Uye unokwanisa kutsungirira sei pane chinhu chausingazivi?”
  18,69,"Musa akati: “Kana Allah vada, uchandiwana ndakatsungirira, uye handikutadziri kana chii zvacho.”"
  18,70,"(Al-Khidr) akati: “Kana ukanditevera, usandibvunze chipi zvacho kusvika ndakutaurira.”"
  18,71,"Naizvozvo vakaenderera mberi kusvika vakakwira ngarava, (Al-Khidr) akaiboora. Musa akati: “Waiboora kuti unyudze vanhu vayo? Zvirokwazvo, waita chinhu chakaipa!”"
  18,72,"Akati (Al-Khidr): “Handina kukuudza here kuti haukwanisi kutsungirira neni?”"
  18,73,"(Musa) akati: “Ndiregererewo pane zvandakanganwa, uye usava unondiomesera nenyaya yangu.”"
  18,74,"Naizvozvo vakaenderera mberi kusvika vasangana nemukomana, uye (Al-Khidr) akamuuraya. Musa akati: “Wauraya munhu akanaka asina kuuraya munhu? Zvirokwazvo, waita chinhu chakaipa!”"